author: Whitney Medworth
title: Steph Curry's birthday cake is the most Steph Curry birthday cake
text:
It has his mouthguard! Ew!
It’s Stephen Curry’s 29th birthday and he has a cake, a typical birthday celebration. But the cake is decorated a bit strange, if you ask me.
Blessed to see another year. So many things to be thankful for! Keep growing, keep pushing, living life....Appreciate everyone who reached out today. #29 #morelife 
A post shared by Wardell Curry (@stephencurry30) on Mar 14, 2017 at 6:04pm PDT 
It has the pi symbol, which is fine because it’s Pi Day. (Cake is better than pie though) It has Steph Curry’s own logo, sure. IT HAS A MOUTHGUARD. WHY PUT A MOUTHGUARD ON A CAKE. WHO PUT A MOUTHGUARD ON A CAKE. NO MOUTHGUARDS ON CAKES. Besides this terrible/great cake, Steph also had some kids singing to him courtside before the game, which was pretty darn cute.
Happy Birthday, Steph!
